No, no, don't do that, not

00:12.041 --> 00:15.333
while I'm on. Bring it with you!

00:15.375 --> 00:20.542
Take your TV out for a glorious

00:15.375 --> 00:20.542
afternoon of non-stop sunshine!

00:20.583 --> 00:24.375
(  ominous theme playing  )

00:24.417 --> 00:27.333
Don't worry,

00:24.417 --> 00:27.333
not even a little rain

00:27.375 --> 00:29.500
can dampen this beautiful day.

