Get in and wait for backup.

01:08.125 --> 01:10.291
Hey, hey,

01:08.125 --> 01:10.291
I was making rescues

01:10.333 --> 01:11.834
before you set foot

01:10.333 --> 01:11.834
on this planet.

01:11.875 --> 01:13.834
I think I can handle

01:11.875 --> 01:13.834
a little mud.

01:16.875 --> 01:21.208
How about a lot of mud?

